content.rendered:
Ok truth be told, I really do my makeup the same every single time I do it, and I don’t reallllly know how to do it any other way. So I wanted to share with you all my makeup products I use every day. NOTHING is sponsored or anything like that, I genuinely use all of this and love every single product!! Hope you enjoy!

First things first, wash and moisturize your face. I love makeup wipes for before and after putting on my makeup!

Smashbox Photo Finish Primer: After I moisturize, I feel like it helps my makeup go on smoother!

Philosophy Concealer: The thing that I put over my acne betttterrrr also be okay for my skin, so this is my fav concealer. It really covers up my acne and doesn’t bother my skin or dry it out. 

Maybelline Fit Me Dewy Smooth Foundation: Omg, my friend just gave this to me (bc she has so much of it), and it’s AHHHmazing. Fav foundation ever.

Bobbi Brown: I use a lighter bronzer of Bobbi Brown to set the foundation and give a light brush over my skin.

Smashbox highlighter, bronzer and blush palette: I can’t live withoth this. It’s small enough to fit in my makeup bag and has the BEST color tints. I love how all my highlighter, bronzer for my contour, and then my blush is in one spot. Plus, this golden highlighter is my favorite type of highliter. I don’t like using something more silver. I think this palette is the reason I look so beachy!

There are TWO eye shadow palettes I like. This one more for night time:

Smashbox Vlada Palette: love the colors, but have glitter and the darks could be too dark for day time. I like using the rust color shadow but not during the day. LOVE this brown though!

NYX Palette: During the day, this palette doesn’t have glitter (in the top three at least) and it’s more natural colors. I like the pinkish tone during the day.

(as you can tell I REALLY use all this stuff hahaha)

Fav every occasion lip color:

Chella Eyebrow Pencil, Taupe color: Then, I am currently out of this product at the moment, and literally have had to borrow all my friends eye brow pencils HAHA but this has been my go to eye brow pencil for 2 years.

Loreal Voluminous mascara: Last but not least, I think I’ve been using this for years! I’m sure there might be better out there, but I really don’t know lol:

YAY!! Thanks for reading! Again, nothing sponsored, just want to really take you through what I use because I get asked!!

xx Katie
